        "content": "<p>206. 撰寫程式碼說明氣泡排序bubble sort如何提早結束執行。<br />\r\nvoid bubbleSort(int A[], int n ){</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; bool sorted = False ;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; for(pass = 1; pass &lt;n &amp;&amp; != sorted; ++pass){</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; sorted = TRUE;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; for(int index = 0; index &lt; n-pass; index++){</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; if(A[index]&gt; A[index+1]){</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; swap(A[index], A[index+1]);</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; sorted = FALSE;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; }</p>\r\n\r\n<p>}</p>\r\n\r\n<p>多加一個bool值去判斷是否排好序，只要有一次交換就把bool值改成false。當資料量大時，原時間複雜度O(n<sup>2</sup>)能變成O(n)。</p>",
